{"type": "article", "id": 10610, "title": "Zick Zack 桌子", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235816zlQF4orWS3p2dCO5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如果你对简单利落的几何形状、混合材料等元素的设计感兴趣，可以了解一下 波兰设计师 <a href=\"http://bielawska.de/\" target=\"_blank\">Olga Bielawska</a> 的作品，她毕业于著名的魏玛鲍豪斯大学，随着展览越来越多而愈发受到关注。2015 年米兰设计周，她展出了两款设计。其中之一就是 <a href=\"http://bielawska.de/products/zick-zack/\" target=\"_blank\">Zick Zack 桌子</a>。由低光泽感且粉末涂层的钢板激光切割后制作，外表有粉末涂层。几何形状非常简单粗暴，挺有美感，适合很现代的家居环境。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235815942AwqKBaMTZRz76.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235815o3b4OTnUZd8zBrcR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94603175\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235816p8G3ILYhXzwVaPjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75749319\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}